modules.description: This module configures and installs a trace collector for capturing execution traces. It provides `collector` to retrieve the trace collector instance and `setup` to install it, enabling trace collection during program execution. It works with the `Trace.collector` type to facilitate integration with tracing infrastructure.

This module tracks execution spans for profiling, allowing creation, annotation, and coloring of spans with associated text, numeric values, and plots. It works with integers as span identifiers and supports thread naming, messages, and formatted output. Concrete use cases include instrumenting functions to measure performance, adding contextual annotations to spans, and visualizing metrics in profiling tools.
